headline: Archer Daniels to Report Q1 Earnings: What Should Investors Expect?
summary: ADM's first-quarter 2025 results are likely to reflect the impacts of tough market conditions and higher costs. A soft Ag Services & Oilseeds segment is also a concern.

headline: Stay Ahead of the Game With ADM (ADM) Q1 Earnings: Wall Street's Insights on Key Metrics
summary: Evaluate the expected performance of ADM (ADM) for the quarter ended March 2025, looking beyond the conventional Wall Street top-and-bottom-line estimates and examining some of its key metrics for better insight.
